Name: Gothicc Breaker
About the game: Gothicc Breaker is the classic Brick Breaker game, but with a background that is not... flat! Break the blocks and reveal the picture that lies beneath. Unlock new levels and test your luck, and once you are done go check out the gallery, to see what you have unlocked! Get Ready for your fresh new Goth GF!
